---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Bitcoin Kids" description="Educational projects for children of all ages focused on Bitcoin, economics, and freedom technology.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bitcoin Kids</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A collection of fantastic educational projects for children of all ages designed to supercharge their skills in science, technology, engineering, maths, and money.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4">
          If you are an educator focused on Bitcoin and freedom technology and would like to be included on this list, please get in <a href="mailto:oink@lightningpiggy.com" class="text-pink hover:underline font-semibold">touch</a>.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Education Hubs -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Education Hubs</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              <a href="https://x.com/BTCJuniorClub" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-pink transition-colors">Bitcoin Junior Club →</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Education-fun zone for kids, teens & parents alike. All things Bitcoin in one place.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              <a href="https://www.bitcoin4youth.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-pink transition-colors">EconoKidz →</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">An animated course that introduces children to essential economic concepts, money, and Bitcoin. Perfect as a supplement to any homeschool or traditional school curriculum, EconoKidz is designed for kids aged 8 and up, parents, teachers, or anyone interested in these fascinating topics. Narrated by two young Bitcoiners aged 8 and 9, this free resource is both engaging and educational.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entrepreneurial Inspiration -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Entrepreneurial Inspiration</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              <a href="https://beehappyfarm.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-pink transition-colors">Bee Happy Farm →</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Nineveh is a 9-year-old who is home-educated and lives in a lovely house with a spacious garden full of animals. She cares for three cats, two goats, 18 chickens, two ducks, and about 50,000 bees! With a deep passion for animals, Nineveh aspires to become a veterinarian. At Bee Happy Farm, she and her helpers offer child-friendly experience days where they provide tours and share fascinating information about all the animals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Games -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Games</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              <a href="https://sites.google.com/nathanday.net/gamertron/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-pink transition-colors">Gamertron →</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Awesome Bitcoin Games by <a href="https://x.com/sambonzuki" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-pink hover:underline">Sam</a> & <a href="https://nostr.com/nprofile1qqsvfa085adgecmg84ffelcxx6zrn3ffu5jrc6cjtwng0zge3ptv43c82kf5d" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-pink hover:underline">Nathan</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              <a href="https://github.com/LightningPiggy/ZapNotify" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-pink transition-colors">ZapNotify →</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              <a href="https://oink.lightningpiggy.com" class="text-pink hover:underline font-semibold">Give us an Oink!</a> Experience a new and engaging way to fuel our FOSS project, brought to life by <a href="https://github.com/ThomasFarstrike" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-pink hover:underline">Thomas Farstrike</a>. This web app triggers sound alerts, pop-ups, and more each time a contribution is zapped via the lightning network. Give it a try and hear the difference your support makes, in real-time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
